result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :visible="visible"
  :keyboard="false"
  :maskClosable="false"
  okText="保存"
  okType="primary"
  @ok="handleOk()"
  @cancel="handleCancel()">
  <a-form
    :form="form">
    <a-form-item
      label="建筑名称"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}"
      v-bind="layout">
      <a-input
        type="text"
        v-decorator="[
          'name',
          {
            rules:[
              { required: true, message: '请输入名称' },
              { max:32, message: '长度在32个汉字以内' }
            ],
            validateTrigger: 'blur',
            initialValue: record ? record.name : null
          }
        ]">
      </a-input>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="奖项"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="city"
        v-decorator="[
              'awards',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.awards:'1'}
            ]">
        <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">市级</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">省级</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">国级</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="基础"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="1"
        v-decorator="[
              'base',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.base:'1'}
            ]">
        <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">不合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">严重不合格</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="主体"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="1"
        v-decorator="[
              'mainBody',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.mainBody:'1'}
            ]">
        <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">不合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">严重不合格</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
    <a-form-item
      label="装饰"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="1"
        v-decorator="[
              'decorate',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.decorate:'1'}
            ]">
      <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">不合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">严重不合格</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
     <a-form-item
      label="屋面"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="good"
        v-decorator="[
              'roofing',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.roofing:'1'}
            ]">
        <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">不合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">严重不合格</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
     <a-form-item
      label="防水"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="good"
        v-decorator="[
              'waterproof',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.waterproof:'good'}
            ]">
       <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">不合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">严重不合格</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
     <a-form-item
      label="保温"
      :label-col="{span: 8}"
      :wrapper-col="{span: 12}">
      <a-select
        placeholder="请选择"
        option.initialValue="good"
        v-decorator="[
              'insulation',
              {rules: [
              {required: true, message: '请选择状态'}
              ],
              initialValue: record?record.insulation:'good'}
            ]">
       <a-select-option :key="1" value="1">合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="2" value="2">不合格</a-select-option>
        <a-select-option :key="3" value="3">严重不合格</a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>

  </a-form>
</a-modal>
